      "bgName": "tokyoconference-00-noon",
      "startTime": 9.1791158836
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ai",
      "speakerName": "小美山愛",
      "speakerNameEn": "Ai",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-ai.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ai_09_01/sud_vo_adv_card_ai_09_01-ai001.m4a",
      "text": "はぁ～……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Haa…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 9.1791158836,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ai_09_01/sud_vo_adv_card_ai_09_01-koh002.m4a",
      "text": "……愛？　おーい、愛。聞いてるか？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "…Ai? Hey~ Ai? Are you listening?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 11.6101366322,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyoconference-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyoconference-00-noon",
      "startTime": 16.67043161
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ai",
      "speakerName": "小美山愛",
      "speakerNameEn": "Ai",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-ai.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ai_09_01/sud_vo_adv_card_ai_09_01-ai002.m4a",
      "text": "はっ！？　す、すみません！\n仕事が終わったら、全力で走って帰ります！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Huh!? S-sorry!\nI’ll run back with all my might after work!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 18.3333337784,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyoconference-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyoconference-00-noon",
      "startTime": 22.1612707417
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ai_09_01/sud_vo_adv_card_ai_09_01-koh003.m4a",
      "text": "いや、送っていくって言ったんだけど……\n全然聞いてないじゃないか。どうしたんだ？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "No‚ I said I’d take you…\nYou’re not listening at all. What’s wrong?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 25.4162373431,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyoconference-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyoconference-00-noon",
      "startTime": 29.3491846045
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ai",
      "speakerName": "小美山愛",
      "speakerNameEn": "Ai",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-ai.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ai_09_01/sud_vo_adv_card_ai_09_01-ai003.m4a",
      "text": "すみません、集中出来てなくて……\n私ってほんとダメダメですね……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Sorry‚ I couldn’t concentrate…\nI’m so useless…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 32.1957707704,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ai_09_01/sud_vo_adv_card_ai_09_01-koh004.m4a",
      "text": "……愛？　もしかして、何か悩みがあるのか？\n俺で良ければ聞くけど",
      "translations": {
        "en": "…Ai? Is something bothering you?\nYou can talk to me if you want.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 39.8666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyoconference-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyoconference-00-noon",
      "startTime": 41.9902064919
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ai",
      "speakerName": "小美山愛",
      "speakerNameEn": "Ai",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-ai.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ai_09_01/sud_vo_adv_card_ai_09_01-ai004.m4a",
      "text": "いえ！　なんでもないんです、本当に\n私は大丈夫ですから！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "No! It’s nothing‚ really.\nI’m totally fine!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 44.9051062296,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ai_09_01/sud_vo_adv_card_ai_09_01-koh005.m4a",
      "text": "……分かった、でも何かあったらいつでも頼ってくれ\n打ち合わせ、続けて大丈夫か？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "…Okay. But if something’s wrong‚ don’t hesitate to tell me.\nCan we continue the meeting?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 52.0000004451,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyoconference-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyoconference-00-noon",
      "startTime": 54.9406124233
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ai",
      "speakerName": "小美山愛",
      "speakerNameEn": "Ai",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-ai.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ai_09_01/sud_vo_adv_card_ai_09_01-ai005.m4a",
      "text": "大丈夫です！　本当にすみませんでした！\nちゃんと走って帰りますから！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I’m fine! I’m really sorry!\nI’ll run back properly!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 58.1000004451,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ai_09_01/sud_vo_adv_card_ai_09_01-koh006.m4a",
      "text": "（やっぱり全然聞いてない……心配だな）",
      "translations": {
        "en": "（She’s not listening at all… I’m worried.）",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 60.6564400154,
      "sfxList": [
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_walk-out-single-01.m4a",
          "delay": 6676.893763000003,
          "startTime": 67.3333337784
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyotown-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyotown-00-noon",
      "startTime": 66.526784861
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyotown-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyotown-00-noon",
      "startTime": 66.526784861
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ai",
      "speakerName": "小美山愛",
      "speakerNameEn": "Ai",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-ai.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ai_09_01/sud_vo_adv_card_ai_09_01-ai006.m4a",
      "text": "お疲れ様です、{user}さん……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Good work‚ {user}-san…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 68.1434505104,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ai_09_01/sud_vo_adv_card_ai_09_01-koh007.m4a",
      "text": "愛、どうしたんだ？　ふらふらじゃないか\nもしかして体調が悪いのか？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Ai‚ what’s wrong? You’re stumbling.\nAre you feeling unwell?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 75.9267896601,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyotown-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyotown-00-noon",
      "startTime": 78.4009543378
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ai",
      "speakerName": "小美山愛",
      "speakerNameEn": "Ai",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-ai.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ai_09_01/sud_vo_adv_card_ai_09_01-ai007.m4a",
      "text": "い、いえいえ！　どこも悪くなんてありませんよ！\nほら、元気一杯です～……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "N-no! I’m perfectly fine!\nSee? I’m full of energy~…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 82.5000004451,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyotown-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyotown-00-noon",
      "startTime": 85.6203904111
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ai_09_01/sud_vo_adv_card_ai_09_01-koh008.m4a",
      "text": "言ったそばからふらふらしてるじゃないか\n本当になんともないのか？　熱でもあるんじゃないか？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "You’re stumbling as we speak.\nAre you sure you’re alright? Maybe you have a fever?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 88.2648410756,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ai",
      "speakerName": "小美山愛",
      "speakerNameEn": "Ai",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-ai.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ai_09_01/sud_vo_adv_card_ai_09_01-ai008.m4a",
      "text": "なんともありませんから\nほんのちょっぴり、疲れが溜まってる、だけで……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I’m fine.\nJust a little… tired…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 94.4666671117,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyotown-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyotown-00-noon",
      "startTime": 98.8680743496
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ai",
      "speakerName": "小美山愛",
      "speakerNameEn": "Ai",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-ai.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ai_09_01/sud_vo_adv_card_ai_09_01-ai009.m4a",
      "text": "お、お仕事中は気合いと根性で乗り切りますから！\n大丈夫ったら大丈夫ですから！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I-I’ll power through it with spirit and guts while working!\nI’m telling you‚ I’m fine!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 103.5000004451,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyotown-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyotown-00-noon",
      "startTime": 106.967893215
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ai_09_01/sud_vo_adv_card_ai_09_01-koh009.m4a",
      "text": "……本当に、どうしたんだ？　ちゃんと教えてくれ\nこのままじゃ仕事には行かせられない",
      "translations": {
        "en": "…Seriously‚ what’s wrong? Tell me properly.\nI can’t let you work like this.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 111.8666671117,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyotown-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyotown-00-noon",
      "startTime": 114.4897982558
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ai",
      "speakerName": "小美山愛",
      "speakerNameEn": "Ai",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-ai.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ai_09_01/sud_vo_adv_card_ai_09_01-ai010.m4a",
      "text": "うぅ、分かりました。お仕事が終わったらお話しします\nで、でも、本当に大丈夫ですから、任せて下さい！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Uuu‚ okay. I’ll tell you after work.\nB-but‚ I’m really fine‚ so please‚ trust me!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 121.5666671117,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ai",
      "speakerName": "小美山愛",
      "speakerNameEn": "Ai",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-ai.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ai_09_01/sud_vo_adv_card_ai_09_01-ai011.m4a",
      "text": "よ～し、今日も頑張りますよ～！\nそれでは、現場に向かいましょう！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "A-alright! I’m going to do my best today~!\nNow‚ let’s head to the location!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 130.2000004451,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ai_09_01/sud_vo_adv_card_ai_09_01-koh010.m4a",
      "text": "（……仕方ない。愛に無理をさせないよう）\n（俺が気をつけよう）",
      "translations": {
        "en": "（…It can’t be helped. I’ll have to keep an eye on Ai）\n（so she doesn’t overdo it.）",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 137.3000004451,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_dressingroom-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "dressingroom-00-noon",
      "startTime": 140.0668008448
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_dressingroom-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "dressingroom-00-noon",
      "startTime": 140.0668008448
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ai",
      "speakerName": "小美山愛",
      "speakerNameEn": "Ai",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-ai.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ai_09_01/sud_vo_adv_card_ai_09_01-ai012.m4a",
      "text": "……お疲れ様でした\n結局ミスばかりで、本当にすみません……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "…Good work.\nI’m really sorry‚ I ended up making so many mistakes…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 143.9000004451,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ai_09_01/sud_vo_adv_card_ai_09_01-koh011.m4a",
      "text": "愛、お疲れ様。足を見せてくれ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Ai‚ good work. Let me see your leg.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 148.6760525665,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_dressingroom-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "dressingroom-00-noon",
      "startTime": 152.3387963416
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ai",
      "speakerName": "小美山愛",
      "speakerNameEn": "Ai",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-ai.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ai_09_01/sud_vo_adv_card_ai_09_01-ai013.m4a",
      "text": "えっ！？　{user}さん、こんな所で\nいきなり何言い出すんですか……！？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "What!? {user}-san‚ why are you\nsaying that here all of a sudden…!?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 154.7258120419,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
